data.description: SELLER NOW OFFERING $5K IN BUYER CONCESSIONS! 3040 Sparks Rd is the property you've been waiting for! This spacious home sits back from the street on 3 acres, making it private & creating a serene surrounding. As you approach the home, you are greeted w/ a large covered front porch for you to drink your morning coffee. The family room has a nice vaulted ceiling & woodburning FP. There are 3 BRs on the same level, w/ 2 BRs sharing a jack-n-jill bathroom. The dining room off the kitchen has numerous windows allowing lots of light into the home. There is plenty of cabinet space in the kitchen, a breakfast bar & sliding door leading out to the back deck. Master BR has a walk-in closet & master bath has a beautiful walk-in shower and soaking tub. Downstairs is a large open space w/ 2 closets & half bath. This can be used as a playroom, 4th BR, office or rec room. You can also access the backyard from downstairs. The backyard has a fenced-in play area, making it perfect for children or pets.  2 covered sheds are also in the backyard, with 1 containing an abundance of firewood for this winter. Plenty of land to explore and do whatever you want with.
